Detailed Description

cvmx_pip_frm_len_chk#

Notes: PIP_FRM_LEN_CHK0 is used for packets on packet interface0, PCI, PCI RAW, and PKO loopback ports. PIP_FRM_LEN_CHK1 is unused.
